This product includes software originally developed by foolz and contributors.

Changes made by kvf77 relative to the original work include (but are not limited to):
  - Relicensed namespace from Foolz\SphinxQL to Kvf77\Manticore.
  - Added orWhere() and nested where() groups (Closure) with arbitrary nesting depth.
  - Added REGEX() filter support to the WHERE clause (Manticore-specific).
  - Unified and simplified the WHERE compiler (AND/OR/groups/regex).
  - Added valuesAmount() helper.
  - Modernised the codebase for PHP 8.3+ (declare(strict_types=1), etc.).
  - Removed the external illuminate/database coupling from the core.

